---
<Layout 
title="Best trout fishing spots near Gresham, Oregon"
description="Comprehensive guide to the best trout fishing hotspots – with seasonal tips, gear suggestions, and local insights."
url="https://gresham.oregonfishingforum.com/trout/best-spots/"
type="article"
